{"tid":1577027,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【香港民間議會】權力要歸於人民，就必須成立香港民間議會！","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:39:24.000Z","uid":158270,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9ecc441fd76a5227ddd0659fb8e4b6a5a3fa37","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"自西伐利亞民族國家誕生以來，只有擁有主體性嘅民族先至有生存嘅資格，先有成為國際社會一員嘅資格，先有對抗他國欺侮嘅資格。法國、英國成功由絕對君主制渡過為人民授權嘅政府，係因為佢哋成功統合國內唔同團體嘅民族認同，哈布斯堡王朝、鄂圖曼帝國、俄羅斯帝國、蘇維埃社會主義共和國聯盟嘅解體亦係由於佢哋嘅領地嘅人民出現咗同宗主國統治相違背嘅民族覺醒。<br />\n中國作為泱泱大國，又係社會主義先鋒兼人民嘅救星，只要共產黨肯企喺人民嘅一邊，應該相信香港人可以治理好香港。<br />\n香港人民亦不應妄自菲薄，認為自己嘅聲音微不足道。我相信大家聚首一堂，商議同表決議案可以支持各種行動組。想支持嘅人可以表態支持，俾行動嘅人知道自己嘅舉措得到社會支持；想行動嘅人亦都知道自己行動嘅成效大概係幾多。甚至我哋可以聯合一起對政府嘅一啲政策提出意見。<br />\n經過多月來的洗禮，目前香港人已經具備思想準備同動機，正式兌現前國家領導人鄧小平「港人治港，高度自治」的政治承諾。<br />\n<br />\n香港民間議會，現正籌辦當中。實名認證，匿名投票，一切資料皆保密妥當。就算俾人偷到資料，都只會得到一串亂碼。程序已備，只差最後一步，成個框架就告成。<br />\n欲知詳情，請到 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkparliament\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkparliament&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5L%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=1b7006f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkparliament</a> 了解。<br />\n<br />\n原po<br />\n<br />\n[ UPDATE ] 建立民間議會進度01<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f74fac6828541f588f39f2d77f84838f9095b145","tid":1577027,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"31449bae93c24a46a2e60bdcf89615c1ad60eca9","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74fac6828541f588f39f2d77f84838f9095b145","tid":1577027,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"The direction is the same"},{"pid":"ac90545a137b185e422ffe577c0c6a1ff35e323a","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd84baf6e12d4514820471c381ee518be056f279","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da52321ce0058a70929f252621c470efe369dac5","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82adaecd705e49182cfcbb6637df1f53c23f3315","tid":1577027,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d737afd98d5fd262088ce3602fb0c99fe02f2e6d","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d33dda271961d4efedbb484393d99e195d7b987","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5e3b537185c86d69b903a5b8f8a1bc150286801","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8325e2d34732361b99174db20352962748cf749","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d83cac64d46e0878d15b61da863b39bee9f73062","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d61e0e06f02ddb01519d47fe06a23a62ad08d26","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbe85c156f72e9ea0e44557bf8f36d01f3994bcd","tid":1577027,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54b1e7e06f3ea4